high_descs: Turn around and walk across to the sink
Pick up the egg from the left side of the sink
Turn around and walk over to the fridge
Put the egg in the fridge then remove it
Turn around and walk back over to the sink
Open the microwave above the sink and put the egg in it
anns.task_desc: Put the egg in the microwave

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the egg to the left of the sink.
Turn around and veer left to the fridge.
Place the egg in the fridge in front of the potato. Close the door, wait a moment, and then take it out again.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Look up and place the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled egg in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn to your right, take a step, turn right again, and go to the sink
Pick up the egg by the left side of the sink basin.
Turn right, take a few steps, turn right again, and go to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the egg on the tray, close the fridge, wait for 5 seconds, and take out the egg from the fridge
Go back to the sink with the egg, and move it up
Put the egg inside the microwave above the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled egg in the microwave
